      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 13:17:01 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.kontronn.com/post/soc/amd-next-generation-chips-will-use-3nm-and-4nm-manufacture-technology.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
